---
title: American Cheesy Beef Enchiladas with Tomato Salsa & Yoghurt
description: Go stateside tonight by adding All-American flavours to a beef filling for enchiladas. Sneak some veggies into the mix, smother the lot with cheese, top it off with a fresh tomato salsa and you're good to go. That's all, folks!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/american-beef-enchiladas-2a3d86bf.jpg
